export type Tag =
  | 'html'
  | 'body'
  | 'h1'

  | 'tbody';

// Is the element rendered as a "Text" tag
export const isText: Record<Tag, boolean> & Record<string, boolean> = {
  html: false,

  span: true,

  b: true,
  strong: true,
  q: true,
  i: true,
  em: true,
  u: true,
  s: true,
  cite: true,
  dfn: true,
  code: true,
  abbr: true,
  sup: true,
  sub: true,

  a: false,
